<author>sḥr gẖbwr, sḥr gẖbwr</author>
<title>ạ̉qwyạʾ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉qwyạʾ fy ạlmsyḥ ạ̉qwyạʾ
 1- mn ạlʿạlm ạ̉qwy̱ mn ạlsẖyṭạn ạ̉ʿly̱ klạmh lnạ
 bh yqynnạ yjʿlnạ ạ̉ḥkm mn kl ạlạ̉ʿdạʾ ạ̉qwyạʾ
 2- kl ywm llạ̉mạm nmsk bạlyd ạlzmạm slṭạnh lnạ
 wrwḥh lnạ qwtnạ hy mn ạlʿlạʾ ạ̉qwyạʾ
 3- frs lywm ạlqtạl bnạ yṣnʿ ạlmḥạl nsyr bạlạ̹ymạn
 wnhzm ạlʿyạn njạḥnạ mn ạ̹lh ạlsmạʾ ạ̉qwyạʾ</lyrics>
</song>